{"id":4157,"date":"2025-06-16T13:38:24","date_gmt":"2025-06-16T06:38:24","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/?p=4157"},"modified":"2025-06-16T13:38:24","modified_gmt":"2025-06-16T06:38:24","slug":"nen-dung-sua-rua-mat-sang-hay-toi","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/thong-tin-nganh\/nen-dung-sua-rua-mat-sang-hay-toi\/","title":{"rendered":"N\u00ean d\u00f9ng s\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t s\u00e1ng hay t\u1ed1i? D\u00f9ng khi n\u00e0o t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">L\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch da l\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc quan tr\u1ecdng trong quy tr\u00ecnh ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da h\u00e0ng ng\u00e0y. Tuy nhi\u00ean, c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi <\/span><\/i><b><i>&#8220;n\u00ean d\u00f9ng s\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t s\u00e1ng hay t\u1ed1i&#8221;<\/i><\/b><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> v\u1eabn khi\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u0103n kho\u0103n. M\u1ed7i th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m trong ng\u00e0y c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng kh\u00e1c nhau \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00e0n da, v\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u00fang th\u1eddi gian s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng s\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t s\u1ebd gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n duy tr\u00ec l\u00e0n da s\u1ea1ch v\u00e0 kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh. C\u00f9ng GSC t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u c\u00e1ch s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng s\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 mang l\u1ea1i hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1i \u01b0u cho l\u00e0n da c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n nh\u00e9!<\/span><\/i><\/p>\n\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"nen-dung-sua-rua-mat-nhu-the-nao-tung-thoi-diem-trong-ngay\"><\/span><b>N\u00ean d\u00f9ng s\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o t\u1eebng th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m trong ng\u00e0y?<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 th\u00f3i quen s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u00f9ng m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1i s\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t c\u1ea3 s\u00e1ng v\u00e0 t\u1ed1i. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1i \u01b0u cho l\u00e0n da, b\u1ea1n n\u00ean ch\u1ecdn c\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m kh\u00e1c nhau cho m\u1ed7i th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m trong ng\u00e0y. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khuy\u00ean t\u1eeb c\u00e1c chuy\u00ean gia da li\u1ec5u gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn s\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p:<\/span><\/p>\n<ol>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Bu\u1ed5i s\u00e1ng: V\u00e0o bu\u1ed5i s\u00e1ng, da ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf b\u1ee5i b\u1ea9n v\u00e0 d\u1ea7u th\u1eeba t\u00edch t\u1ee5 trong \u0111\u00eam. S\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9 pH th\u1ea5p v\u00e0 c\u00f4ng th\u1ee9c d\u1ecbu nh\u1eb9 s\u1ebd gi\u00fap l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m m\u1ea5t \u0111i \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean c\u1ee7a da.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Bu\u1ed5i t\u1ed1i: Sau m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y d\u00e0i ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac v\u1edbi \u00f4 nhi\u1ec5m, l\u1edbp trang \u0111i\u1ec3m, v\u00e0 c\u00e1c y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00e1c, b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n d\u00f9ng s\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch s\u00e2u h\u01a1n. S\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u00fat b\u1ee5i b\u1ea9n v\u00e0 d\u1ea7u th\u1eeba s\u1ebd gi\u00fap l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng v\u00e0 ng\u0103n ng\u1eeba m\u1ee5n.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"huong-dan-chon-sua-rua-mat-phu-hop-voi-tung-loai-da\"><\/span><b>H\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn ch\u1ecdn s\u1eeda r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi t\u1eebng lo\u1ea1i da<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u200b\u200bM\u1eb7c d\u00f9 vi\u1ec7c l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch da b\u1eb1ng s\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t l\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n trong quy tr\u00ecnh ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da. Nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i lo\u1ea1i da n\u00e0o c\u0169ng y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u00e1ch s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng gi\u1ed1ng nhau. H\u00e3y c\u00f9ng t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u c\u00e1ch s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng s\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p cho t\u1eebng lo\u1ea1i da. \u0110\u1ec3 t\u1ed1i \u01b0u h\u00f3a hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n:<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4158\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4158\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4158\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/64-1.webp\" alt=\"ch\u1ecdn s\u1eeda r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi t\u1eebng lo\u1ea1i da\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/64-1.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/64-1-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/64-1-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/64-1-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4158\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Ch\u1ecdn s\u1eeda r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi t\u1eebng lo\u1ea1i da<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"chon-sua-rua-mat-cho-da-thuong\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ch\u1ecdn s\u1eeda r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t cho da th\u01b0\u1eddng<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Da th\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00e0 lo\u1ea1i da d\u1ec5 ch\u0103m s\u00f3c v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 kh\u00f4 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 d\u1ea7u, c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean. N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n s\u1edf h\u1eefu l\u00e0n da n\u00e0y, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y may m\u1eafn v\u00ec vi\u1ec7c l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch kh\u00e1 \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n. Ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t 2 l\u1ea7n m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y, v\u00e0o bu\u1ed5i s\u00e1ng v\u00e0 bu\u1ed5i t\u1ed1i, l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef da s\u1ea1ch s\u1ebd v\u00e0 tho\u00e1ng m\u00e1t m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng lo b\u1ecb m\u1ee5n hay t\u1eafc ngh\u1ebdn l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">V\u00e0o bu\u1ed5i s\u00e1ng: S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng s\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf d\u1ea7u th\u1eeba m\u00e0 da s\u1ea3n sinh ra trong su\u1ed1t \u0111\u00eam. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y gi\u00fap da b\u1ea1n c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y t\u01b0\u01a1i m\u1edbi, tho\u00e1ng kh\u00ed v\u00e0 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u00f3n ng\u00e0y m\u1edbi.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">V\u00e0o bu\u1ed5i t\u1ed1i: Sau m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y d\u00e0i ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac v\u1edbi b\u1ee5i b\u1ea9n, d\u1ea7u nh\u1eddn v\u00e0 l\u1edbp trang \u0111i\u1ec3m, b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch s\u00e2u h\u01a1n. H\u00e3y b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c t\u1ea9y trang n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 trang \u0111i\u1ec3m, sau \u0111\u00f3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng s\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ec3 lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00e1c t\u1ea1p ch\u1ea5t v\u00e0 gi\u00fap da th\u01b0 gi\u00e3n. Cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, h\u00e3y lau kh\u00f4 da v\u00e0 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng kem d\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u1ea9m \u0111\u1ec3 duy tr\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"sua-rua-mat-cho-da-dau\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">S\u1eeda r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t cho da d\u1ea7u<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Da d\u1ea7u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1eed th\u00e1ch trong vi\u1ec7c ch\u0103m s\u00f3c v\u00ec l\u01b0\u1ee3ng d\u1ea7u nh\u1eddn d\u01b0 th\u1eeba d\u1ec5 g\u00e2y m\u1ee5n, t\u1eafc ngh\u1ebdn l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng v\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn da d\u1ec5 b\u00e1m b\u1ea9n. N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 l\u00e0n da d\u1ea7u, vi\u1ec7c ch\u0103m s\u00f3c v\u00e0 l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch da \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ec3 duy tr\u00ec l\u00e0n da kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 s\u1ea1ch s\u1ebd.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4159\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4159\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4159\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/64-2.webp\" alt=\"S\u1eeda r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t cho da d\u1ea7u\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/64-2.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/64-2-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/64-2-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/64-2-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4159\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">S\u1eeda r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t cho da d\u1ea7u<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">L\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch da \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch: \u0110\u1ec3 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng d\u1ea7u th\u1eeba v\u00e0 ng\u0103n ng\u1eeba m\u1ee5n, b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 2 l\u1ea7n m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y v\u1edbi s\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t chuy\u00ean d\u1ee5ng cho da d\u1ea7u. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y gi\u00fap lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf b\u1ee5i b\u1ea9n, d\u1ea7u th\u1eeba v\u00e0 ng\u0103n ng\u1eeba t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng t\u1eafc ngh\u1ebdn l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Tr\u00e1nh c\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u d\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u1ea9m: M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u1ea9m r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi da d\u1ea7u, b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i s\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t c\u00f3 th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n d\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u1ea9m qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u. Nh\u1eefng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m t\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng d\u1ea7u tr\u00ean da, khi\u1ebfn t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng &#8220;b\u00f3ng nh\u1eaby&#8221; tr\u1edf n\u00ean t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7 h\u01a1n.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"sua-rua-mat-cho-da-kho\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">S\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t cho da kh\u00f4<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Da kh\u00f4 th\u01b0\u1eddng thi\u1ebfu s\u1ee9c s\u1ed1ng, d\u1ec5 b\u1ecb n\u1ee9t n\u1ebb v\u00e0 bong tr\u00f3c, \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi m\u1ed9t ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 ch\u0103m s\u00f3c \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ec3 duy tr\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m v\u00e0 tr\u00e1nh g\u00e2y th\u00eam t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng cho da. \u0110\u1ec3 ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da kh\u00f4 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3, vi\u1ec7c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng s\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4161\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4161\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4161\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/64-4.webp\" alt=\"S\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t cho da kh\u00f4\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/64-4.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/64-4-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/64-4-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/64-4-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4161\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">S\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t cho da kh\u00f4<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng s\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t v\u00e0o bu\u1ed5i t\u1ed1i: Da kh\u00f4 ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y, v\u00e0o bu\u1ed5i t\u1ed1i, \u0111\u1ec3 lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf b\u1ee5i b\u1ea9n, vi khu\u1ea9n v\u00e0 t\u00e0n d\u01b0 c\u1ee7a l\u1edbp trang \u0111i\u1ec3m. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y gi\u00fap da \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m m\u1ea5t \u0111i l\u1edbp d\u1ea7u t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean, gi\u00fap da th\u01b0 gi\u00e3n v\u00e0 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho vi\u1ec7c d\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u1ea9m v\u00e0o ban \u0111\u00eam.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">R\u1eeda m\u1eb7t v\u00e0o bu\u1ed5i s\u00e1ng ch\u1ec9 b\u1eb1ng n\u01b0\u1edbc l\u1ea1nh: V\u00e0o bu\u1ed5i s\u00e1ng, b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i d\u00f9ng s\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t, ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t b\u1eb1ng n\u01b0\u1edbc l\u1ea1nh \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m m\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean tr\u00ean da. Sau \u0111\u00f3, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng kem d\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u1ea9m \u0111\u1ec3 cung c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m cho da su\u1ed1t c\u1ea3 ng\u00e0y.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"sua-rua-mat-cho-da-nhay-cam\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">S\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t cho da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m r\u1ea5t d\u1ec5 b\u1ecb k\u00edch \u1ee9ng v\u00e0 d\u1ecb \u1ee9ng, v\u00ec v\u1eady vi\u1ec7c ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u00fang s\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t l\u00e0 v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng quan tr\u1ecdng. \u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng b\u1ea1n s\u1edf h\u1eefu l\u00e0n da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m, l\u1eddi khuy\u00ean t\u1eeb c\u00e1c chuy\u00ean gia l\u00e0 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng s\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t qu\u00e1 th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4160\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4160\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4160\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/64-3.webp\" alt=\"S\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t cho da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/64-3.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/64-3-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/64-3-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/64-3-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4160\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">S\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t cho da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng s\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t v\u00e0o bu\u1ed5i t\u1ed1i: N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m, ch\u1ec9 n\u00ean s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng s\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t v\u00e0o bu\u1ed5i t\u1ed1i, khi l\u00e0n da c\u1ea7n l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch sau m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y d\u00e0i ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac v\u1edbi b\u1ee5i b\u1ea9n v\u00e0 vi khu\u1ea9n. Ch\u1ecdn s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m d\u1ecbu nh\u1eb9, kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ee9a h\u01b0\u01a1ng li\u1ec7u hay c\u1ed3n, gi\u00fap l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m da b\u1ecb t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean d\u00f9ng s\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t v\u00e0o bu\u1ed5i s\u00e1ng: V\u00e0o bu\u1ed5i s\u00e1ng, da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t b\u1eb1ng s\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t. Ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi n\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ea1ch \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap da d\u1ecbu nh\u1eb9 v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m da m\u1ea5t \u0111i l\u1edbp b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean. Vi\u1ec7c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng s\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t v\u00e0o bu\u1ed5i s\u00e1ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m da y\u1ebfu \u0111i, d\u1ec5 b\u1ecb k\u00edch \u1ee9ng v\u00e0 d\u1ec5 b\u1eaft n\u1eafng.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"ket-luan\"><\/span><b>K\u1ebft lu\u1eadn<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u00e2u h\u1ecfi &#8220;<\/span><b><i>n\u00ean d\u00f9ng s\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t s\u00e1ng hay t\u1ed1i<\/i><\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">&#8221; kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n l\u00e0 v\u1ec1 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng, m\u00e0 quan tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n, b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00fang lo\u1ea1i da c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. \u0110\u1ec3 c\u00f3 l\u00e0n da kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 tr\u00e1nh c\u00e1c v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 nh\u01b0 k\u00edch \u1ee9ng hay m\u1ee5n, h\u00e3y ch\u0103m s\u00f3c \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch v\u1edbi s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p.<\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>M\u1ed7i th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m trong ng\u00e0y c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng kh\u00e1c nhau \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00e0n da, v\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u00fang th\u1eddi gian s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng s\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t s\u1ebd gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n duy tr\u00ec l\u00e0n da s\u1ea1ch v\u00e0 kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":7,"featured_media":4162,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[16],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-4157","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-thong-tin-nganh"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4157","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/7"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=4157"}],"version-history":[{"count":1,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4157\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":4163,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4157\/revisions\/4163"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/4162"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=4157"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=4157"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=4157"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}